kurum-info\"><span class=\"kurum-name\">Sağlık Bakanlığı</span><span class=\"kurum-desc\">saglik.gov.tr</span></div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square k-link-icon\"></i>\n                </a>\n                <a href=\"https://www.toki.gov.tr\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"kurum-card\" data-n=\"TOKİ Toplu Konut İdaresi konut\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                    <div class=\"kurum-emblem\">🏠</div>\n                    <div class=\"kurum-info\"><span class=\"kurum-name\">TOKİ</span><span class=\"kurum-desc\">toki.gov.tr</span></div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square k-link-icon\"></i>\n                </a>\n                <a href=\"https://www.kyk.gov.tr\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"kurum-card\" data-n=\"KYK Kredi Yurtlar Kurumu burs yurt\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                    <div class=\"kurum-emblem\">🎒</div>\n                    <div class=\"kurum-info\"><span class=\"kurum-name\">KYK</span><span class=\"kurum-desc\">kyk.gov.tr</span></div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square k-link-icon\"></i>\n                </a>\n                <a href=\"https://www.diyanet.gov.tr\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"kurum-card\" data-n=\"Diyanet İşleri Başkanlığı\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                    <div class=\"kurum-emblem\">☪️</div>\n                    <div class=\"kurum-info\"><span class=\"kurum-name\">Diyanet İşleri Başkanlığı</span><span class=\"kurum-desc\">diyanet.gov.tr</span></div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square k-link-icon\"></i>\n                </a>\n                <a href=\"https://www.tika.gov.tr\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"kurum-card\" data-n=\"TİKA Türk İşbirliği Koordinasyon Ajansı\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                    <div class=\"kurum-emblem\">🌐</div>\n                    <div class=\"kurum-info\"><span class=\"kurum-name\">TİKA</span><span class=\"kurum-desc\"